      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONE MORE BUTTON (8) is a sprinter who thrives over these shorter races. Last start was fourth over 390m at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 (22.64). Has a strong winning record here at the trip including two wins. Can make amends. OLLIE DEEDS (2) was below best at his last start when 8th at Warrnambool following a third place finish (17.85) at this track two back. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should be in this for a long way. CADILLAC LANDAU (1) finished sixth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 305m at this track, taking a Invitation in a swift 17.73. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. KIWI TO BURN (6) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
